content: RT @TeamTrumpPOWERFUL: President Trump is joined by Patty Morin, the mother of Rachel Morin, who was murdered by an illegal alien while out on a run near her home in Maryland.Her daughter would be alive today if Kamala Harris had done her job.Listen to her heartbreaking story.
